title: AoE4's (Free) New Civs! What we know so far...

media:group.media:title: AoE4's (Free) New Civs! What we know so far...
media:group.media:description:
Two new civilizations have been announced: Malians and Ottomans. Even more surprising, they're free for all Age of Empires 4 players. 

Source: https://www.ageofempires.com/news/age-iv-anniversary-update-oct-25/ 

How to play for free: Download Age of Empires IV from Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1466860/Age_of_Empires_IV/
or buy from Steam or Microsoft Store https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/age-of-empires-iv/9n94ncgm1q2n
